    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/c8f2b0e36c79b844616ea8b79d2eca91.poster.avif?t=1741688879\" width=800 height=184 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/c8f2b0e36c79b844616ea8b79d2eca91.webm?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/c8f2b0e36c79b844616ea8b79d2eca91.mp4?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/8cfae1e680fe153386785b0b6d4dc861.avif?t=1741688879\" width=600 height=90 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/9235935e8971a04e8abaa36b6e068980.poster.avif?t=1741688879\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/9235935e8971a04e8abaa36b6e068980.webm?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/9235935e8971a04e8abaa36b6e068980.mp4?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Seven Times To Die&quot; is an exhilarating 2D top-down action RPG with engaging roguelite and deckbuilding elements, set in a captivating high fantasy world on the brink of invasion by other realms. Immerse yourself in a richly detailed universe where every decision, every drawn card, and every battle is a test of skill, strategy, and deck mastery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/ec9154adee25121f2a5dedfc4bf866e6.avif?t=1741688879\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/4b418be43c8b2661a83c0af4a98be1de.poster.avif?t=1741688879\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/4b418be43c8b2661a83c0af4a98be1de.webm?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/4b418be43c8b2661a83c0af4a98be1de.mp4?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this world, you are granted seven lives—precious resources that must be used wisely throughout your journey. The game's deep progression systems allow for extensive buildcrafting, enabling you to design unique decks and character builds tailored to your preferred playstyles. From casting powerful spells to wielding formidable weapons, the freedom to shape your strategy is vast and impactful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/518ac00846d8705e5e77aa8daa27f2d3.avif?t=1741688879\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/6c8751add9e3a2c2e02d35da4f3ee088.poster.avif?t=1741688879\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/6c8751add9e3a2c2e02d35da4f3ee088.webm?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/6c8751add9e3a2c2e02d35da4f3ee088.mp4?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat is complex yet rewarding, with a strong focus on deckbuilding and card sequencing. Players can assemble decks before each run, selecting the best combinations for the challenges ahead. During battles, cards are drawn at intervals, allowing players to cast them in sequence from left to right, with the order influencing the outcome of each action. Modifier cards add an extra layer of strategy, altering the effects of cards to their right and creating powerful synergies that can turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/60024eaa56c82dbd1792b870346a5d86.avif?t=1741688879\" width=600 height=90 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/e1ed450ce8213c8e361eee15b5c8def7.poster.avif?t=1741688879\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/e1ed450ce8213c8e361eee15b5c8def7.webm?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/e1ed450ce8213c8e361eee15b5c8def7.mp4?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every encounter pushes your skills to the limit, from relentless hordes of evil creatures to epic boss fights that test your tactical prowess and deck management. The tension rises as each life you lose brings you closer to the brink of failure—but also offers an opportunity to refine your strategy, adapt your deck, and come back stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/8f5e45404a54bd4c1dfbd7c98bbedd25.avif?t=1741688879\" width=600 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/9df1824620c3a0651c109e3c5dad4039.poster.avif?t=1741688879\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/9df1824620c3a0651c109e3c5dad4039.webm?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090830/extras/9df1824620c3a0651c109e3c5dad4039.mp4?t=1741688879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you fight to repel the invading forces and save your homeland from destruction, every life lost raises the stakes, but also enhances the potential for legendary heroism. &quot;Seven Times To Die&quot; demands cunning, courage, and mastery of both combat and cards. Your mission is clear: defend the realm, harness the power of your decks, and prove that you have what it takes to save the world from annihilation. Will you rise as a legend, or fall to the invasion? The fate of the realm lies in your hands, and every card you play could be the difference between victory and defeat.</p>",
